2.1. Gene Ontology Analysis

Enrichment Analysis Gene Ontology

##  Cellular Component
ego.cc <- enrichGO(gene        = gene.df$ENSEMBL,
                 OrgDb         = org.Hs.eg.db,
                 keyType       = 'ENSEMBL',
                 ont           = "CC",
                 pAdjustMethod = "BH",
                 pvalueCutoff  = 0.01,
                 qvalueCutoff  = 0.05)
